Description: # wgpu-py
        
        A Python lib wrapping the Rust wgpu lib and exposing it with a WebGPU compatible API.
        
        This is experimental, work in progress, you probably don't want to use this just yet!
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
Requires-Python: >=3.6.0
